 badet kom han i kontakt med ekstremt giftig irukandji-manet , men fikk rask legebehandling og slapp med skrekken."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|kuriosa"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "eedbd2faa1ba77ee900e5e957c2dcb074d4abb6f022af3e377f38f13861405c5"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-09T00:48:05.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Skulle blogge om hvor bra det var \u00e5 bo australsk \u00f8y - men fikk aldri tid til \u00e5 kose seg."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1339067.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/jobb_"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ca9ebcaaae084dd880138f66eed4024959974e07.jpg?58c0a645"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Ben (34) ble utslitt av \u00abverdens beste jobb\u00bb -adressa.no", "Travelt", "19 timers arbeidsdag"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "ca9ebcaaae084dd880138f66eed4024959974e07"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "kuriosa"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "hamilton island"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "jobb"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["the sunday telegraph", "queensland", "the daily telegraph"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "ben southall"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/kuriosa"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1339067.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/jobb_"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Ben (